//     → 提 nativeurl/talker/sender/msgid → 存红包运行态(内存 Map, attempt=0) → delay(rp_first_sec×1000) → hbProcess
//   hbProcess(nativeurl): 启动器拉封面页 NewReceiveUI。
//   NewReceiveUI.onResume: delay 后 UI 有界查找 detail 入口("看看大家的手气"/"查看领取详情" 且可点)
//     ├─ 可点且含"手气"(拼手气领完) → performClick → 微信流转 NewDetailUI
